Package: brgast
Type: Package
Title: Break-Regime Generalized Autoregressive Score Models for Tail Risk
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Open", "Source", email = "opensource@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Author: Open Source [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Open Source <opensource@example.com>
Description: Implements a break-regime generalized autoregressive score model
    with Student-t innovations for one-step-ahead Value-at-Risk and Expected
    Shortfall forecasting. The package is designed to help users fit the core
    model, generate rolling forecasts, and work with a bundled synthetic sample
    dataset without reproducing the full empirical workflow of the associated
    paper.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
URL: https://github.com/Fin-stats/brgast
BugReports: https://github.com/Fin-stats/brgast/issues
